{"title": "Cold Processor Quality Gate -- structured Groq schema + quality_score filter", "description": "Two related gaps from D4 (Prompt Engineering) and D5 (Context & Reliability): (1) Cold processor Groq prompts use freeform JSON extraction with no schema -- brittle, fails silently when Groq outputs unexpected format. (2) hot_reflection quality scores are assigned by single-pass Groq call with no validation gate -- low confidence reflections (quality<0.6) are processed identically to high-quality ones. Architect signal: add JSON schema to Groq prompts + add quality gate before cold processor processes a hot.", "subtasks": "{
  "25.A": {
    "title": "Add JSON output schema to cold processor Groq prompts",
    "status": "pending",
    "items": [
      "25.A.1 Read current Groq prompt in run_cold_processor() in core_train.py",
      "25.A.2 Add explicit JSON schema block to prompt: define expected fields (patterns: list[str], quality_score: float, gaps: list[str], themes: str)",
      "25.A.3 Add JSON parse with fallback: if Groq output fails json.loads, log mistake and skip batch -- never silently corrupt",
      "25.A.V1 core_py_validate passes",
      "25.A.V2 patch_file -> deploy -> build_status green",
      "25.A.V3 trigger_cold_processor -> railway_logs_live -- confirm structured JSON output no parse errors",
      "25.A.GATE Schema added, no parse errors -> proceed to 25.B"
    ]
  },
  "25.B": {
    "title": "Add quality gate: skip hots with quality_score < 0.5 in cold processor",
    "status": "pending",
    "items": [
      "25.B.1 In run_cold_processor() batch fetch: add filter quality_score=gte.0.5 to hot_reflection query",
      "25.B.2 Log skipped low-quality hots count in cold processor summary",
      "25.B.3 Add health_flag: if >30% of unprocessed hots are below 0.5 quality -> flag low_quality_backlog",
      "25.B.V1 core_py_validate passes",
      "25.B.V2 patch_file -> deploy -> build_status green",
      "25.B.V3 debug_fn run_cold_processor dry_run=true -- quality gate visible in preflight",
      "25.B.GATE Quality gate active -> proceed to task_gate"
    ]
  },
  "task_gate": {
    "items": [
      "TGATE.1 Subtasks 25.A and 25.B done",
      "TGATE.2 E2E: trigger cold processor, verify JSON parse succeeds, verify low-quality hots skipped",
      "TGATE.3 railway_logs_live -- no errors",
      "TGATE.4 ping_health passes",
      "TGATE.5 changelog_add called",
      "TGATE.6 notify_owner -- cold processor structured schema + quality gate live",
